  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">The time period for which we keep information varies according to the purpose for which it is used for In some cases there are legal requirements to keep data for a minimum period Unless there is a specific legal requirement for us to keep the information we will retain it for no longer than is necessary for the purposes for which the data was collected or for which it is to be further processed</evidence>
